title: Stephen King-I Know What You Need
description: I Know What You Need" is a short story by Stephen King, first published in the September 1976 issue of Cosmopolitan,Told from the perspective of a popular, college-age girl named Elizabeth Rogan, the premise of this story concerns her sudden, unexpected attraction to a social outcast named Ed Hamner, Jr., whose paranormal ability to perceive what will make any person happy has not resulted in his own................
